@startuml state-transcoding-job
title Transcoding Job — State Diagram

[*] --> Queued : Job created

Queued --> Processing : Worker picks up job

Processing --> Completed : All variants generated
Processing --> Failed : ffmpeg error / timeout

Failed --> Retrying : retryCount < maxRetries
Retrying --> Processing : Worker retries job

Failed --> [*] : maxRetries exceeded\n(permanent failure)
Completed --> [*] : Variants registered

state Processing {
  [*] --> Transcoding360p
  Transcoding360p --> Transcoding480p : 360p done
  Transcoding480p --> Transcoding720p : 480p done
  Transcoding720p --> GeneratingThumbnail : 720p done
  GeneratingThumbnail --> [*] : thumbnail saved
}

note right of Processing
  progress % updated
  after each quality
  variant completes
end note

note right of Failed
  Error details stored
  in TranscodingJob.error
end note

@enduml
